game.name: Kitty Diver
game.description:
Oh my God! This cute kitty has lost her multiple seashells deep in the sea. For this reason, she is now unable to swim and reach to the surface. Can you help her to find all the lost seashells? If yes, join Kitty Diver and be prepared to guide her under the sea. She will be happy enough if you find all the golden seashells for her. All you need to do is just put your eyes on the screen and clear away the blocks of ice in the right order. 
Your efforts will help the kitty move upwards and you will complete the level instantly. Make sure to click on all the multiple types of objects to get her rolling in the right direction. Keep your eyes on the deadly bombs, fish or other hindrances that you see in in the sea! You can clear the path for the kitty by using the planks and mines. Do not forget to look at the sharp objects that help kitty to complete her diving suit in this fun physics puzzle game. 
There are 16 unique and addictive levels to play through in this cool HTML5 platform game. Good luck to destroy all the obstacles that you see along the way while paying attention to grab all the shells to make her reach to the surface safely to complete all the levels! Our website is full of multiple free adventure games that you can try out to improve your brain power and skill while giving you some matchless thrilling hours.
